Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 我到底還能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了改變那如狹隘庭園般的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還活不到人生的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗 相擁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在無意識中被刻上的經驗紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當站在懸崖邊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦難抓住了我的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往更加寬廣的領域\N往更深更大的某處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝著無法預測的世界前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And lt's calling me again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.55,0:01:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11月26日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.67,0:01:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16時37分在太平洋地區出現的D-1被擊毀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.76,0:01:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方的損失為
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潛水艇一艘、飛機5架
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.56,0:01:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件結束後5A級O.P.A.R.T.S被收回
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17時，發現有O.P.A.R.T.S異常反應
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.27,0:01:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到現在也未能阻止那種\N發光現象和石化現象
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:02:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來必須出席委員會議了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.66,0:02:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別無選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是諸位責任的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.54,0:02:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是作為負責人的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外，我們應把昨天擊毀的Dolem的\N殘骸提交給上面…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件東西是很有說服力的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它能證明由TERRA使用5A會有多好的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.35,0:02:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此，\N現在不是參加委員會議的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐，所謂政治就是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管功刀司令並不喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了現在這個階段\N好像5A已經和他同步了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.44,0:02:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個，他現在在哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要一個能夠採集他處於\N融合狀態時數據的設備
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真的很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.64,0:03:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名綾人，\N今天工作結束了，你下床吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.04,0:03:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣，準備好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令，我把綾人君帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛，他們兩個怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像小孩子賭氣似的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那個男孩不是很可愛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從昨天的檢驗結果看，\N你的身體好像沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是說他很高興你沒有受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.55,0:04:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經決定了你的住處
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…紫東大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你帶他去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼綾人君，咱們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來他討厭這裡的每一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是這樣的話，讓我送他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，我不是這裡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:04:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣行了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我們被將了一軍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是次序問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙小姐，下面我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠，你有時間嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實有點事想拜託你，可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的，什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.16,0:05:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不愛說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，總比說廢話好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽過MU的歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一種優美的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:05:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有絲毫的冗繁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MU？Churchwared寫到過的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:01.77,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}James Churchward(1851-1936):\N美國作家，1931年出版《失落的大陸——MU》一書，MU大陸學說的支持者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是傳說，但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.15,0:06:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都這麼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每件事物都需要名字吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天感覺怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的醫生真討厭，\N如果我真的健康的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不需要每天接受檢查了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，今天能回家嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我來這裡接你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝，哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是前扣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是根來彼方的海灣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根來彼方？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:56.37,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}根來彼方：原文為「 」，官方翻譯為「根來彼方」\N日本西南諸島傳承著這樣的傳說，每年神都會從名叫\N「 」的理想鄉而來，帶給人們豐收和幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沖繩傳說中的理想鄉嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:59.75,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「 」的意思就是「大海彼岸的理想鄉」\N從語源學的角度來講，「」是指「（我們所來的）根源之地」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你雖然年輕但是倒是知道的不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前面的根來島上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些為調查遺跡而建的\N人造結構建築物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,構成了海上試驗城市——神至市
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:12.34,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}神至市：原文市，官方翻譯為神至市
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看，就是右邊那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以叫做根來彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一個有趣的雙關語吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀司令的專機\N看來他會在關西地區工作一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了你那在奈利亞遺跡的RahXephon\N不被那些討厭的傢伙打擾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:37.58,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}奈利亞（）遺跡：「」是「」的別稱，因此得名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧，它是屬於你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定對功刀司令有不少誤解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.05,0:07:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是功刀司令的別墅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他看起來有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實，他非常有人情味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個院子裡的樹是櫻樹…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算是島上的名勝了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年春天我第一次被邀請…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常美麗的櫻花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是神名綾人君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，久遠小姐，你的行李
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是錄有D-1詠歎調的碟片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新曲子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正在這裡做音樂研究
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…她是你的夫人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜子是我最好的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡只有我妹妹和我兩個人住，\N什麼時候你都可以來玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人，要是也住在這裡就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久遠小姐會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.57,0:09:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要帶你去的住處比這裡更好，我保證
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我妹妹別看她那樣，其實很怕生的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那塊肉還沒烤熟吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生啤！一扎！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.76,0:09:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就開始喝？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喝的是烏龍茶吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一扎生啤！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是軍人，\N對任務有疑問的話找你們上司去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被不是自己上司的人利用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.87,0:09:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要把那個男孩變成你的道具嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經被你誣陷了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你和那個工具的關係惡化，\N真的沒什麼辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:10:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許一個好女人比一個好人更容易成為他的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對他的管理這麼寬鬆行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他的生理節律和精神狀態\N正在加速這種石化現象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼必須先讓他解開心結
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使對他進行電擊，\N也是不能讓這種現象停止的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像給你準備了一些用得上的日用品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓邊上的洞洞堵住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收容所還有多遠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想TERRA很重視你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這個島不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是有很刺激的事件發生，\N而且空氣新鮮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:10:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚也很美味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的車要開上這個坡道碼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，不…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，你晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊，我遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.06,0:11:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…你已經到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要住在她家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我家，是我叔叔家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾我會住在那裡，\N你不要太高興了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼口氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇，你品味真差…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.04,0:11:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.25,0:11:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，兩個年輕人，\N後面的事情你們自己安排吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:11:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.26,0:12:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我特意買來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡和東京
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你家很不一樣吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.15,0:12:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能你暫時還不習慣\N就當去親戚家玩，輕鬆一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事我不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前從沒去過親戚家玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，惠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到吃晚飯還有一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶綾人君到周圍看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.47,0:12:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？我平時不是教你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:13:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個，你的叔叔平時都說些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要住我們家？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.56,0:13:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很為難…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓人家覺得因為和我吵架你才離開的好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會很為難的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘！彈珠汽水！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喝？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有這裡的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別盯著我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是，請用…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了，你的手帕…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別和我那麼親密
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外，姐姐和我們一起住，\N你別想偷襲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看，那個不去上學的女孩在約會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不上學？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你有時候在軍隊工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過不要你的手帕！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那也沒關係…\N至少你現在還有容身之處
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你是攝影師？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，畫家…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢，\N一個想成為畫家的高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？這麼說在Tokyo Jupiter裡也有高中嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.66,0:16:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想回東京？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在我也沒什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.47,0:16:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只顧自己一個人喝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，不過那個好喝嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道彈珠汽水嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然知道，但是沒喝過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小球堵著根本喝不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好笑的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:17:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋，要把小球移到凹坑裡去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好涼爽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.74,0:17:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西誰會穿啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾菲來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不是你家吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.77,0:17:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要吐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.77,0:17:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，等等，要吐嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.36,0:17:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:17:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布奇？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跑哪兒去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小寶貝！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說小惠的姐姐是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.36,0:18:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生啤！來一扎！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是老闆娘啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢，魚很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如月博士跟我說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根來彼方是一個好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛的小男生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天還說他是無聊的男孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要「鎖定」姐姐我嗎？「鎖定」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後讓我們「纏鬥」到明天早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「纏鬥」！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人君，能過來一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點事要麻煩你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…六道先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我叔叔就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你經常教導小惠是什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「己所不欲，勿施於人」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓她常記於心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個掛在門口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個，叔叔…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在幾點？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.07,0:20:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好涼爽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找小惠是找對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.77,0:20:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，一點問題也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是一個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，我們會照顧他的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我梳頭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們常說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.56,0:21:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花那樣紅是因為樹下埋著屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為吸取了屍體的血液\N櫻花才如此鮮艷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀司令院子裡的櫻花\N綻放出的鮮艷的藍色難以言喻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.54,0:21:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道在那院子裡埋著什麼人？

Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.56,0:23:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌唱的極光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.44,0:23:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦澀的回憶,從記憶深處浮現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.07,0:23:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon第六樂章
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.95,0:23:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅都市
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.74,0:23:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界飽含著聲音


